# List GitHub issues in ascending order (oldest first) for the spring-2025 repository
gh issue list --repo mgelberg/spring-2025 --search sort:created-asc 

# Start time tracking and link to issue when pushing commits
# 1. Start the timer: gh issue comment <issue-number> --body "/spend 0h" 
# 2. When done, update with total time: gh issue comment <issue-number> --body "/spend <hours>h"
# Example: gh issue comment 123 --body "/spend 2h 30m" 